{"tid":1555353,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"國歌應該每日六點半都響起","createTime":"2019-09-09T10:24:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T10:50:08.000Z","uid":189338,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ec36ce8959fd159017c94fd93f08afb5aa84a571","tid":1555353,"uid":189338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T10:24:24.000Z","msg":"細個對中國認識唔多<br />\n但都對中國有一定嘅歸屬感<br />\n因為每日食飯時間 六點半新聞前 tvb 就會播國歌 又讚美中國文化幾美好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n歸屬感呢啲野真係要由小建立 而且要日日播 日日做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：岩呀 要日日播到大家都識唱<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：點止每日六點半播 無時無刻都要播啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />近排有首歌幾正 順面係到分享吓<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/y7yRDOLCy4Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fy7yRDOLCy4Y&d=8Se%2B9W40ah4Gl3auq3G%2Buvkum5iQZutveDYoRIbm5C0%3D&h=85dedaac\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/y7yRDOLCy4Y</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LmmTwvU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLmmTwvU.jpg&h=835d7278&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8ec601f51829d2b52310a2c3250a120efa115f51","tid":1555353,"uid":258370,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T10:25:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f5900673de47862a697f5803cc55d310fd0052ac","tid":1555353,"uid":189338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T10:29:01.000Z","msg":"何以 這土地 淚再流"},{"pid":"9245d709b52391380d3c49bbba03a0b1efb75af5","tid":1555353,"uid":189338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f5900673de47862a697f5803cc55d310fd0052ac","tid":1555353,"uid":189338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T10:29:01.000Z","msg":"何以 這土地 淚再流"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T10:29:20.000Z","msg